00:01:46,689 --> 00:01:48,989
=Episode 16=

17
00:01:53,312 --> 00:01:54,930
The Heart-Devouring Poison
comes from the desert

18
00:01:55,832 --> 00:01:57,111
and Mu Haiyao hails from there.

19
00:01:58,152 --> 00:01:59,632
Madam Rou, you must know this, right?

20
00:02:01,912 --> 00:02:02,632
Of course I'm aware.

21
00:02:04,791 --> 00:02:07,071
I never imagined that,
I'm intelligent and loyal, however,

22
00:02:08,310 --> 00:02:10,570
I would meet my end at the hands
of the person I trusted the most.

23
00:02:11,632 --> 00:02:13,191
It was the poison planted by Mu Haiyao,

24
00:02:14,071 --> 00:02:15,991
which was why you followed
Li Qianmo's orders.

25
00:02:17,551 --> 00:02:19,631
Xu Liangchuan is her servant now.

26
00:02:20,392 --> 00:02:21,752
She knows the reason behind this.

27
00:02:22,152 --> 00:02:23,872
She should also know the antidote.

28
00:02:24,090 --> 00:02:25,670
The Heart-Devouring Poison
is very mysterious.

29
00:02:25,991 --> 00:02:27,991
Even the one who administered it
can't cure it.

30
00:02:29,191 --> 00:02:30,392
What Xu Liangchuan knows

31
00:02:31,191 --> 00:02:32,711
is just how to control
the poison's effects.

32
00:02:33,592 --> 00:02:36,392
The most crucial ingredient is placenta.

33
00:02:37,152 --> 00:02:39,560
I've heard that Tinglan Pavilion
has been emitting a foul odour lately.

34
00:02:40,071 --> 00:02:41,232
This should be the source.

35
00:02:44,472 --> 00:02:45,752
I thought highly of myself,

36
00:02:47,551 --> 00:02:49,152
but I was reduced to a pawn

37
00:02:49,152 --> 00:02:49,952
in Li Qianmo's hands.

38
00:02:50,752 --> 00:02:51,152
I hate it.

39
00:02:58,592 --> 00:02:59,560
I had no attachment nor fear.

40
00:03:01,551 --> 00:03:02,911
There's nothing to
be afraid of in death.

41
00:03:04,392 --> 00:03:05,312
However, right now,

42
00:03:08,392 --> 00:03:09,512
I feel remorse towards you

43
00:03:10,631 --> 00:03:11,592
and I wronged you.

44
00:03:12,551 --> 00:03:13,431
You saved me as well.

45
00:03:15,431 --> 00:03:16,831
You risked your life

46
00:03:16,831 --> 00:03:18,170
to stop the vicious dog from harming me.

47
00:03:18,631 --> 00:03:20,512
You harmed me to protect yourself,

48
00:03:21,791 --> 00:03:22,551
but when you saved me,

49
00:03:23,631 --> 00:03:25,312
you were willing to sacrifice yourself.

50
00:03:26,071 --> 00:03:27,551
It was just a momentary impulse.

51
00:03:28,392 --> 00:03:29,312
Don't forget,

52
00:03:30,911 --> 00:03:32,431
I've always been a ruthless poisoner

53
00:03:33,112 --> 00:03:34,791
who kills without hesitation.

54
00:03:35,392 --> 00:03:36,351
You're not.

55
00:03:38,952 --> 00:03:39,472
I once believed

56
00:03:39,472 --> 00:03:41,170
there was no such thing
as sincerity in this world.

57
00:03:43,991 --> 00:03:44,831
However, today,

58
00:03:44,831 --> 00:03:45,831
I unexpectedly encountered it.

59
00:03:52,872 --> 00:03:53,551
Unfortunately,

60
00:03:54,312 --> 00:03:55,032
I'm unfortunate.

61
00:03:57,831 --> 00:03:59,392
My life is already at its end.

62
00:04:00,351 --> 00:04:01,032
Not necessarily.

63
00:04:03,271 --> 00:04:04,472
I said the Heart-Devouring Poison

64
00:04:04,472 --> 00:04:05,592
used to have no cure,

65
00:04:06,752 --> 00:04:07,872
not that it can't be researched.

66
00:04:08,810 --> 00:04:10,070
Young Master granted me the permission

67
00:04:10,280 --> 00:04:12,470
to visit Lianwei Residence freely
for the miscarriage prevention.

68
00:04:12,911 --> 00:04:13,831
Starting tomorrow,

69
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:15,970
you'll visit every three days
for detoxification.

70
00:04:16,351 --> 00:04:17,232
I can't promise you,

71
00:04:17,232 --> 00:04:18,271
but I have a 70% certainty.

72
00:04:18,872 --> 00:04:19,672
Whether you live or die

73
00:04:20,071 --> 00:04:21,112
depends on your destiny.

74
00:04:21,831 --> 00:04:23,991
70% is more than enough.

75
00:04:27,391 --> 00:04:28,592
Even if there's only a 10% chance,

76
00:04:29,511 --> 00:04:30,271
I believe that

77
00:04:30,271 --> 00:04:31,271
if given the opportunity,

78
00:04:31,271 --> 00:04:32,831
we should seize it firmly.

79
00:04:33,912 --> 00:04:34,592
Rou,

80
00:04:35,111 --> 00:04:36,671
you will definitely overcome this.

81
00:04:37,511 --> 00:04:38,632
You'll be alright, I'm sure of it.

82
00:05:03,872 --> 00:05:04,872
Hurry up.

83
00:05:14,271 --> 00:05:15,592
In the future, you must be careful.

84
00:05:16,671 --> 00:05:17,711
Li Qianmo is foolish

85
00:05:18,231 --> 00:05:19,752
and wouldn't have been able to plot this.

86
00:05:20,711 --> 00:05:22,152
To protect this child of yours,

87
00:05:22,711 --> 00:05:23,991
you must be wary of
the person behind,

88
00:05:23,991 --> 00:05:25,510
who has sweet words
and a treacherous heart.

89
00:05:26,312 --> 00:05:26,991
I'm not afraid.

90
00:05:27,671 --> 00:05:28,711
Do you two know

91
00:05:28,912 --> 00:05:31,391
my greatest gain from all this?

92
00:05:35,831 --> 00:05:36,391
It's this.

93
00:05:38,831 --> 00:05:39,991
I didn't want it to come.

94
00:05:41,312 --> 00:05:42,352
I didn't want it to be in

95
00:05:42,511 --> 00:05:43,831
this filthy and complicated place.

96
00:05:44,711 --> 00:05:45,671
Even when

97
00:05:46,032 --> 00:05:48,231
the prince found out and I had to keep it,

98
00:05:48,231 --> 00:05:49,912
I still resisted it a thousand times.

99
00:05:50,951 --> 00:05:52,072
It's been in my belly

100
00:05:52,632 --> 00:05:53,792
for several months already.

101
00:05:54,632 --> 00:05:55,711
I was aware of that,

102
00:05:56,032 --> 00:05:57,271
but I couldn't feel it.

103
00:05:58,752 --> 00:05:59,872
Was it sleeping?

104
00:06:01,032 --> 00:06:01,951
Was it eating?

105
00:06:03,072 --> 00:06:03,951
Was it happy?

106
00:06:04,511 --> 00:06:05,391
What did it look like?

107
00:06:05,391 --> 00:06:06,271
Was it a boy or a girl?

108
00:06:06,671 --> 00:06:07,472
I didn't know at all.

109
00:06:08,592 --> 00:06:09,872
Could a life that I couldn't feel

110
00:06:09,872 --> 00:06:10,711
be considered a life?

111
00:06:12,271 --> 00:06:13,111
However, today...

112
00:06:15,312 --> 00:06:16,511
Today,

113
00:06:16,792 --> 00:06:18,711
when that dog pounced on me,

114
00:06:19,111 --> 00:06:19,872
I realised that

115
00:06:20,511 --> 00:06:21,980
I was not thinking of myself.

116
00:06:21,990 --> 00:06:22,872
I was thinking of it.

117
00:06:25,152 --> 00:06:26,152
I'm not afraid to die.

118
00:06:26,431 --> 00:06:27,391
I'm afraid of hurting it.

119
00:06:28,192 --> 00:06:29,312
That's when I understood

120
00:06:30,551 --> 00:06:33,111
how important it was to me.

121
00:06:36,312 --> 00:06:37,192
It's my flesh,

122
00:06:38,391 --> 00:06:41,352
my blood and my life.

123
00:06:43,312 --> 00:06:46,312
Since I have no family in this mansion,

124
00:06:46,671 --> 00:06:48,072
I'm creating

125
00:06:48,592 --> 00:06:49,551
my own family.

126
00:06:51,352 --> 00:06:52,551
I hope for its birth.

127
00:06:53,912 --> 00:06:55,231
I hope for its growth,

128
00:06:56,312 --> 00:06:58,111
I hope for us to depend on each other.

129
00:07:05,991 --> 00:07:07,192
- Young Master.
- Young Master.

130
00:07:10,152 --> 00:07:11,111
You said

131
00:07:12,032 --> 00:07:13,072
you didn't want

132
00:07:13,711 --> 00:07:14,592
this child for me.

133
00:07:15,831 --> 00:07:17,831
Instead, you're creating a family
for yourself?

134
00:07:23,032 --> 00:07:23,711
Yes.

135
00:07:25,152 --> 00:07:27,671
Even if we have a child together,

136
00:07:28,792 --> 00:07:29,431
you still think

137
00:07:29,551 --> 00:07:31,072
that you have no family in this mansion?

138
00:07:37,991 --> 00:07:38,671
Yes.

139
00:07:39,391 --> 00:07:40,472
Even if you are his mother

140
00:07:40,472 --> 00:07:41,192
and I'm his father,

141
00:07:42,152 --> 00:07:43,752
you still only want to depend on him?

142
00:07:45,991 --> 00:07:46,551
Yes.

143
00:08:10,472 --> 00:08:10,991
I understand.

144
00:08:14,312 --> 00:08:15,511
I know you don't like me coming over.

145
00:08:16,872 --> 00:08:17,711
In that case,

146
00:08:18,991 --> 00:08:19,792
from now on,

147
00:08:19,792 --> 00:08:20,831
I won't come to disturb you.

148
00:08:30,111 --> 00:08:31,032
Shi'er.

149
00:08:31,511 --> 00:08:33,551
Let's sit on the throne, okay?

150
00:08:34,792 --> 00:08:35,192
Come on,

151
00:08:35,551 --> 00:08:36,951
have a seat on that throne, all right?

152
00:08:38,071 --> 00:08:39,992
In the future, you'll become a prince.

153
00:08:42,232 --> 00:08:43,592
Madam. Madam Zhen is here to see you.

154
00:08:48,271 --> 00:08:50,232
Don't cry.

155
00:08:54,672 --> 00:08:55,392
Let her in.

156
00:09:06,680 --> 00:09:08,271
Congratulations for
getting what you wished for.

157
00:09:09,232 --> 00:09:10,631
It's thanks to you.

158
00:09:11,472 --> 00:09:12,352
I'll keep it in mind.

159
00:09:13,391 --> 00:09:14,191
I don't expect you

160
00:09:14,191 --> 00:09:15,232
to remember my kindness,

161
00:09:16,032 --> 00:09:17,432
but I've always been by your side,

162
00:09:17,432 --> 00:09:18,232
singing your praises.

163
00:09:18,552 --> 00:09:20,311
However, my performance
hasn't even started yet

164
00:09:20,552 --> 00:09:21,751
