165
00:09:22,511 --> 00:09:24,511
I really wanted
to see your performance through,

166
00:09:25,711 --> 00:09:26,511
but what you're doing

167
00:09:26,672 --> 00:09:27,951
was against the rules

168
00:09:28,951 --> 00:09:30,232
and there's nothing I could do.

169
00:09:32,511 --> 00:09:33,511
A few days ago,

170
00:09:33,792 --> 00:09:34,631
I asked Zuiliu

171
00:09:34,631 --> 00:09:35,951
to buy some rouge for me.

172
00:09:36,871 --> 00:09:37,592
To my surprise,

173
00:09:37,672 --> 00:09:39,511
when she came back,
she told me something.

174
00:09:40,912 --> 00:09:41,831
She said

175
00:09:42,711 --> 00:09:43,792
she saw you

176
00:09:44,232 --> 00:09:45,432
meeting someone

177
00:09:46,352 --> 00:09:48,432
who looked a lot

178
00:09:49,271 --> 00:09:50,511
like Madam Mei.

179
00:09:50,592 --> 00:09:51,672
How could that be possible?

180
00:09:52,311 --> 00:09:53,391
Since my arrival at the mansion,

181
00:09:53,391 --> 00:09:54,271
I haven't left.

182
00:09:54,951 --> 00:09:56,592
How could I end up at a cosmetics shop?

183
00:09:56,912 --> 00:09:57,792
It's too dark in the alley

184
00:09:57,792 --> 00:09:58,751
and Zuiliu mistook.

185
00:09:58,912 --> 00:09:59,711
Alley?

186
00:10:01,831 --> 00:10:03,152
I never even mentioned an alley.

187
00:10:03,432 --> 00:10:04,912
Why would you even know about it?

188
00:10:05,711 --> 00:10:06,071
I...

189
00:10:07,631 --> 00:10:09,032
Of course I believe in you,

190
00:10:09,792 --> 00:10:10,831
but if Young Master

191
00:10:10,831 --> 00:10:11,912
finds out about this,

192
00:10:12,432 --> 00:10:15,191
I'm afraid he might become suspicious.

193
00:10:18,391 --> 00:10:19,432
You're worrying too much.

194
00:10:20,992 --> 00:10:21,951
You should go back.

195
00:10:22,391 --> 00:10:24,352
The position of the side consort
is still vacant,

196
00:10:25,271 --> 00:10:26,391
and someone should take it.

197
00:10:27,472 --> 00:10:28,391
When the time comes,

198
00:10:29,152 --> 00:10:30,511
many trivial matters

199
00:10:31,191 --> 00:10:32,672
will require your attention.

200
00:10:49,751 --> 00:10:50,391
Umbrellas!

201
00:10:50,391 --> 00:10:51,311
Take a look!

202
00:10:55,152 --> 00:10:55,912
Good.

203
00:11:02,071 --> 00:11:05,032
Finish the entire jar of liquor.

204
00:11:08,032 --> 00:11:09,751
