205
00:11:09,751 --> 00:11:10,912
Let's see what you'll get.

206
00:11:10,912 --> 00:11:11,432
Come on.

207
00:11:11,912 --> 00:11:13,311
I'll give it a try

208
00:11:13,472 --> 00:11:14,870
to see if I can get
something interesting.

209
00:11:25,311 --> 00:11:29,611
(Kill the child in Luo Qinglian's womb.)

210
00:11:42,311 --> 00:11:44,391
Lianxin, please read it.

211
00:11:44,391 --> 00:11:45,552
I'm waiting to draw mine.

212
00:11:46,032 --> 00:11:47,071
