213
00:11:57,951 --> 00:11:59,792
Lianxin, read it.

214
00:12:13,871 --> 00:12:16,472
Kill the child in Luo Qinglian's womb.

215
00:12:18,032 --> 00:12:19,032
Kill...

216
00:12:33,631 --> 00:12:34,352
Lianchu.

217
00:12:34,552 --> 00:12:36,112
I was thinking to take this opportunity

218
00:12:36,112 --> 00:12:37,112
to drink more.

219
00:12:37,432 --> 00:12:38,831
Why are you making such a big joke?

220
00:12:38,831 --> 00:12:39,472
Lianxin.

221
00:12:39,871 --> 00:12:41,912
I've heard that if Luo Qinglian
gives birth to that child,

222
00:12:42,071 --> 00:12:44,552
that child will become
the trueborn grandson of the prince.

223
00:12:48,152 --> 00:12:49,071
Lianchu.

224
00:12:49,871 --> 00:12:50,871
What are you saying?

225
00:12:51,112 --> 00:12:52,511
I dare not even listen to such talk.

226
00:12:53,912 --> 00:12:54,912
The trueborn grandson

227
00:12:55,152 --> 00:12:57,992
can only be your son.

228
00:12:58,672 --> 00:13:00,472
However, I've heard recently

229
00:13:01,232 --> 00:13:03,592
that as long as Luo Qinglian has a child,

230
00:13:04,511 --> 00:13:06,391
you will become the heir.

231
00:13:09,311 --> 00:13:09,831
Lianchu,

232
00:13:11,672 --> 00:13:12,552
you're drunk.

233
00:13:13,391 --> 00:13:13,871
Yes,

234
00:13:14,951 --> 00:13:16,112
Lianchu is drunk.

235
00:13:16,552 --> 00:13:17,592
Lianchu is drunk.

236
00:13:24,152 --> 00:13:25,271
He Lianxin!

237
00:13:31,472 --> 00:13:32,032
Great-uncle.

238
00:13:38,232 --> 00:13:40,112
Look at you,

239
00:13:40,432 --> 00:13:41,552
did Lv Beiyi

240
00:13:42,191 --> 00:13:43,071
refuse to accept the gift?

241
00:13:43,672 --> 00:13:46,631
He didn't even take a look at the mansion.

242
00:13:47,352 --> 00:13:48,232
Not even the money?

243
00:13:49,152 --> 00:13:50,432
He just refused.

244
00:13:50,751 --> 00:13:52,831
He's not the least bit impressed.

245
00:13:52,951 --> 00:13:54,912
Fortunately, we didn't mean to send gifts.

246
00:13:56,951 --> 00:13:57,951
I've heard

247
00:13:58,112 --> 00:13:59,152
that there's a new guest

248
00:13:59,951 --> 00:14:00,951
at Lianwei Residence.

249
00:14:06,472 --> 00:14:08,191
Miss, come here and take a look.

250
00:14:08,391 --> 00:14:09,472
What happened?

251
00:14:11,112 --> 00:14:11,871
What's going on?

252
00:14:11,871 --> 00:14:12,792
Look.

253
00:14:12,792 --> 00:14:14,112
I can't handle it all.

254
00:14:16,112 --> 00:14:16,631
What is this?

255
00:14:19,472 --> 00:14:20,631
Where is she?

256
00:14:20,792 --> 00:14:21,711
You don't have to ask.

257
00:14:21,951 --> 00:14:23,352
She must have worn
something beautiful

258
00:14:23,352 --> 00:14:24,191
and gone out to play.

259
00:14:25,071 --> 00:14:25,792
Miss.

260
00:14:26,071 --> 00:14:27,490
Miss, you're really
spoiling Miss Shuilan.

261
00:14:27,912 --> 00:14:29,550
Madam permitted her to come
to keep you company,

262
00:14:29,631 --> 00:14:30,912
however, she's still a guest.

263
00:14:31,271 --> 00:14:32,480
She's only been here for half a month

264
00:14:32,511 --> 00:14:34,410
and she's already worn
all your clothes and jewellery.

265
00:14:34,792 --> 00:14:38,152
