281
00:15:54,472 --> 00:15:55,672
My sister's things are all mine.

282
00:15:55,912 --> 00:15:56,630
Where are you going?

283
00:15:57,672 --> 00:15:58,792
Back to Lianwei Residence.

284
00:15:59,751 --> 00:16:00,831
You've taken the wrong path.

285
00:16:01,071 --> 00:16:02,112
Lianwei Residence is over there.

286
00:16:02,751 --> 00:16:04,071
Let's go. I'll take you there.

287
00:16:07,937 --> 00:16:09,637
(Lianwei Residence)

288
00:16:13,391 --> 00:16:13,992
Young Master.

289
00:16:16,311 --> 00:16:17,152
We've arrived.

290
00:16:19,912 --> 00:16:20,570
Right, we're here.

291
00:16:20,831 --> 00:16:21,391
Go in.

292
00:16:21,912 --> 00:16:22,912
Aren't you coming in?

293
00:16:23,672 --> 00:16:24,511
No, I have something to do

294
00:16:25,032 --> 00:16:25,831
and must go back first.

295
00:16:26,552 --> 00:16:27,032
All right.

296
00:16:33,511 --> 00:16:33,992
Shuilan.

297
00:16:34,391 --> 00:16:35,352
What's wrong?

298
00:16:40,792 --> 00:16:41,352
Young Master,

299
00:16:42,631 --> 00:16:43,912
it's been several months.

300
00:16:44,311 --> 00:16:45,912
Even if you were mad,
you should've let it go.

301
00:16:46,831 --> 00:16:49,112
Are you really not going
to see Ms. Lian again?

302
00:16:49,511 --> 00:16:50,992
Who said I was angry?

303
00:16:51,152 --> 00:16:52,071
I just can't be bothered.

304
00:16:52,191 --> 00:16:52,912
Women.

305
00:16:54,032 --> 00:16:54,631
Shuilan,

306
00:16:55,490 --> 00:16:56,552
are you afraid of being scolded?

307
00:16:56,552 --> 00:16:57,271
Do you need me

308
00:16:57,271 --> 00:16:58,191
to plead with you?

309
00:16:58,552 --> 00:17:00,232
It's okay. My sister pampers me.

310
00:17:02,472 --> 00:17:03,592
Are you hungry?

311
00:17:03,711 --> 00:17:04,631
Do you want to eat anything?

312
00:17:06,271 --> 00:17:08,552
I'm feeling a bit hungry.

313
00:17:11,152 --> 00:17:13,271
It happens that I'm also a little hungry.

314
00:17:13,912 --> 00:17:15,152
Tell those at the kitchen to prepare

315
00:17:15,231 --> 00:17:17,391
Eight-Treasure Duck, Longan Sweet Soup,

316
00:17:17,792 --> 00:17:19,432
Three Delicacies Meatball
and Lotus Leaf Congee.

317
00:17:19,631 --> 00:17:21,312
Anyway, Ms. Lian said...

318
00:17:28,432 --> 00:17:28,912
Shuilan,

319
00:17:29,312 --> 00:17:30,871
it's getting late. Go in and rest.

320
00:17:32,871 --> 00:17:33,391
All right.

321
00:18:57,471 --> 00:18:58,471
He really got it.

322
00:19:01,391 --> 00:19:02,032
Miss.

323
00:19:02,511 --> 00:19:03,231
I can't help

324
00:19:03,231 --> 00:19:04,032
but say something.

325
00:19:04,552 --> 00:19:05,432
Even if you're angry,

326
00:19:05,631 --> 00:19:06,712
I'll still say it.

327
00:19:07,832 --> 00:19:08,432
Say it.

328
00:19:08,511 --> 00:19:09,432
You can't keep giving Master

329
00:19:09,432 --> 00:19:10,192
the cold shoulder.

330
00:19:10,511 --> 00:19:11,712
After all, he's the child's father.

331
00:19:11,832 --> 00:19:13,391
He's the best father I've ever seen.

332
00:19:13,631 --> 00:19:14,511
In the past six months,

333
00:19:14,591 --> 00:19:17,312
everything we've had at Lianwei Residence,
is as good as Madam Rui's

334
00:19:17,391 --> 00:19:18,751
and better than other servant-concubines'.

335
00:19:18,912 --> 00:19:20,670
Which part of it isn't
because of Master's concern?

336
00:19:21,391 --> 00:19:23,410
Since you made him upset
with those harsh words last time,

337
00:19:23,480 --> 00:19:26,032
I've seen Young Master hesitating
at Lianwei Residence's entrance many times,

338
00:19:26,032 --> 00:19:27,270
but he never comes in for even once.

339
00:19:27,351 --> 00:19:30,111
His affection is so deep
that even the servants are moved.

340
00:19:31,591 --> 00:19:32,351
Miss,

341
00:19:32,580 --> 00:19:34,271
there's just one more month
before you give birth.

342
00:19:34,912 --> 00:19:37,312
Do you really intend to ignore him
for the rest of your life,

343
00:19:37,511 --> 00:19:39,832
preventing the child from ever seeing
its father and mother together?

344
00:19:41,712 --> 00:19:42,792
You've talked so much.

345
00:19:43,271 --> 00:19:44,351
Miss.

346
00:19:46,471 --> 00:19:48,751
I know. I understand.

347
00:19:55,111 --> 00:19:55,712
Child,

348
00:19:57,792 --> 00:19:59,351
do you think I should go or not?

349
00:20:00,072 --> 00:20:02,032
If you think I should, kick me once.

350
00:20:02,672 --> 00:20:05,432
If not, kick me twice.

351
00:20:08,432 --> 00:20:09,032
Did he move?

352
00:20:13,072 --> 00:20:14,231
It moved.

353
00:20:14,231 --> 00:20:15,751
How many times?

354
00:20:15,751 --> 00:20:16,631
How many times, Miss?

355
00:20:21,312 --> 00:20:23,271
Pathetic.

356
00:20:23,952 --> 00:20:25,672
What kind of women have I never seen?

357
00:20:26,032 --> 00:20:27,432
How did I become such a coward?

358
00:20:29,032 --> 00:20:29,672
Young Master.

359
00:21:00,032 --> 00:21:01,152
Slow down.

360
00:21:10,111 --> 00:21:10,912
This is

361
00:21:11,751 --> 00:21:13,351
something I picked up by chance.

362
00:21:13,832 --> 00:21:14,912
It's not valuable.

363
00:21:15,351 --> 00:21:17,391
You can just keep it casually.

364
00:21:17,712 --> 00:21:19,672
If you don't want it,
you can give it to someone else

365
00:21:21,231 --> 00:21:23,152
or even throw it away.

366
00:21:27,991 --> 00:21:29,511
No.

367
00:21:32,591 --> 00:21:33,912
