the character of "red" to "green"?

372
00:22:23,792 --> 00:22:24,631
It's moving.

373
00:22:26,231 --> 00:22:27,471
It often moves.

374
00:22:27,832 --> 00:22:28,672
I feel as if

375
00:22:28,672 --> 00:22:30,111
it understands what we're saying.

376
00:22:30,871 --> 00:22:31,631
Really?

377
00:22:34,471 --> 00:22:35,152
Child,

378
00:22:36,072 --> 00:22:37,231
