379
00:22:38,351 --> 00:22:39,231
Do you like him?

380
00:22:40,072 --> 00:22:41,192
If you like him,

381
00:22:41,471 --> 00:22:42,712
kick him twice for him to listen.

382
00:22:43,871 --> 00:22:44,712
Listen?

383
00:22:59,871 --> 00:23:00,312
Qinglian,

384
00:23:01,792 --> 00:23:03,072
why did he only kick once?

385
00:23:06,111 --> 00:23:06,751
Baby, kick again

386
00:23:06,952 --> 00:23:08,712
so that I can hear it.

387
00:23:09,072 --> 00:23:10,032
Move again, won't you?

388
00:23:11,391 --> 00:23:12,032
Can't you hear

389
00:23:12,032 --> 00:23:13,312
your father talking to you?

390
00:23:14,792 --> 00:23:16,111
Move again.

391
00:23:21,111 --> 00:23:21,871
Miss Shuilan,

392
00:23:22,111 --> 00:23:23,511
