393
00:23:23,511 --> 00:23:24,460
Osmanthus Sweet Ferment Rice.

394
00:23:24,511 --> 00:23:25,271
Try it first.

395
00:23:33,712 --> 00:23:34,712
It's not sweet at all.

396
00:23:35,032 --> 00:23:35,631
Did they forget

397
00:23:35,631 --> 00:23:36,591
to add sugar to my bowl?

398
00:23:37,351 --> 00:23:40,032
It's all made in the kitchen
and distributed to all the houses.

399
00:23:40,471 --> 00:23:41,351
It shouldn't be.

400
00:23:42,152 --> 00:23:43,391
I said it's not sweet.

401
00:23:44,192 --> 00:23:46,170
Isn't there a jar of osmanthus sugar
at Qinglian's place?

402
00:23:46,312 --> 00:23:47,552
Just get it for me.

403
00:23:47,631 --> 00:23:48,712
What a waste.

404
00:23:49,152 --> 00:23:50,032
A waste?

405
00:23:50,952 --> 00:23:52,631
That's a reward
from Young Master to Ms. Lian.

406
00:23:52,871 --> 00:23:54,511
Normally, Ms. Lian doesn't even eat it.

407
00:23:54,631 --> 00:23:55,552
She keeps it in some...

408
00:23:57,072 --> 00:23:58,271
You're a lowly servant.

409
00:23:58,511 --> 00:23:59,832
How dare you look down on me.

410
00:23:59,832 --> 00:24:00,871
How dare you hit me.

411
00:24:00,991 --> 00:24:02,712
Even Ms. Lian has never hit us.

412
00:24:02,832 --> 00:24:03,751
Because she's foolish.

413
00:24:03,751 --> 00:24:04,351
Lan'er!

414
00:24:06,111 --> 00:24:07,072
What else do you want to say?

415
00:24:07,072 --> 00:24:07,751
Ms. Lian.

416
00:24:08,952 --> 00:24:09,351
I...

417
00:24:11,312 --> 00:24:12,312
Apologise to Zhiyue right now.

418
00:24:12,552 --> 00:24:13,391
Apologise?

419
00:24:13,871 --> 00:24:15,391
You want me to apologise to a servant?

420
00:24:15,952 --> 00:24:17,552
Who taught you that?

421
00:24:18,152 --> 00:24:19,672
It's important to know what's right.

422
00:24:20,271 --> 00:24:21,111
They treat you so well.

423
00:24:21,111 --> 00:24:22,231
How can you hit and scold them?

424
00:24:22,312 --> 00:24:23,792
That's right, Ms. Shuilan.

425
00:24:23,912 --> 00:24:25,351
Zhiyue has always been so good to you,

426
00:24:25,351 --> 00:24:27,111
taking care of your daily needs.

427
00:24:27,111 --> 00:24:28,312
Even you dare to scold me.

428
00:24:29,672 --> 00:24:30,991
Both of you are ganging up on me.

429
00:24:31,271 --> 00:24:32,672
You're a pair of shameless servants.

430
00:24:32,672 --> 00:24:33,192
You...

431
00:24:33,432 --> 00:24:34,312
What did you say?

432
00:24:36,832 --> 00:24:38,152
Shameless servants, stupid servants

433
00:24:38,152 --> 00:24:39,391
and despicable servants!

434
00:24:39,631 --> 00:24:39,991
You...

435
00:24:42,952 --> 00:24:43,712
I...

436
00:24:44,231 --> 00:24:44,871
Ms. Lian.

437
00:24:44,871 --> 00:24:46,152
Qinglian, you hit me.

438
00:24:46,231 --> 00:24:47,152
No. Lan'er.

439
00:24:47,152 --> 00:24:47,591
I...

440
00:24:48,792 --> 00:24:49,871
Ms. Shuilan!

441
00:24:53,912 --> 00:24:54,552
Miss.

442
00:25:02,270 --> 00:25:04,270
(Jingshu Hall)

443
00:25:04,471 --> 00:25:05,351
Are you

444
00:25:06,672 --> 00:25:08,351
Ms. Lian's younger sister?

445
00:25:10,271 --> 00:25:12,751
You're so pretty and you're a guest.

446
00:25:14,152 --> 00:25:15,871
Who would make you cry?

447
00:25:23,751 --> 00:25:24,751
Have you calmed her down?

448
00:25:25,552 --> 00:25:26,511
I just showed her

449
00:25:26,511 --> 00:25:27,631
some clothes and jewellery.

450
00:25:27,991 --> 00:25:29,432
Her eyes are glowing.

451
00:25:29,871 --> 00:25:30,832
She's so vain.

452
00:25:31,351 --> 00:25:32,760
Have all the servants
of Lianwei Residence

453
00:25:33,351 --> 00:25:34,192
gone out?

454
00:25:34,631 --> 00:25:35,231
Don't worry.

455
00:25:35,912 --> 00:25:37,271
The others left
at Lianwei Residence.

456
00:25:37,712 --> 00:25:39,192
Luo Qinglian is alone.

457
00:25:40,631 --> 00:25:41,712
I told you

458
00:25:42,712 --> 00:25:44,152
I was patient.

459
00:25:49,552 --> 00:25:50,471
Ms. Shuilan!

460
00:25:50,952 --> 00:25:52,631
Ms. Shuilan!

461
00:25:53,111 --> 00:25:54,871
Ms. Shuilan!

462
00:25:55,152 --> 00:25:55,912
Ms. Shuilan.

463
00:25:57,351 --> 00:25:58,271
Ms. Shuilan!

464
00:25:58,712 --> 00:26:01,192
Have you seen Ms. Shuilan
from Lianwei Residence?

465
00:26:01,792 --> 00:26:02,351
No.

466
00:26:10,032 --> 00:26:10,631
Ms. Lian.

467
00:26:11,032 --> 00:26:13,832
Ms. Shuilan is waiting
for you to pick her up.

468
00:26:13,991 --> 00:26:14,631
What did you say?

469
00:26:14,952 --> 00:26:15,952
Please take a look.

470
00:26:20,111 --> 00:26:20,552
Young Master.

471
00:26:20,751 --> 00:26:21,631
Something has happened.

472
00:26:22,032 --> 00:26:24,991
Madam Zhen is suddenly seriously ill
and bedridden.

473
00:26:45,391 --> 00:26:45,991
What happened?

474
00:26:46,991 --> 00:26:48,192
Come here.

475
00:26:51,511 --> 00:26:52,192
Slow down.

476
00:26:57,432 --> 00:26:57,952
She's awake.

477
00:26:58,192 --> 00:26:58,792
She's awake.

478
00:27:00,192 --> 00:27:00,751
Young Master.

479
00:27:01,672 --> 00:27:02,351
Please don't talk.

480
00:27:03,111 --> 00:27:04,351
You're still weak right now.

481
00:27:04,991 --> 00:27:07,591
I'll ask Lv Beiyi to prepare some medicine
to drive away the cold for you.

482
00:27:11,432 --> 00:27:12,111
Is it here?

483
00:27:14,231 --> 00:27:14,751
Here?

484
00:27:15,991 --> 00:27:16,751
Here.

485
00:27:32,631 --> 00:27:33,432
Are you angry?

486
00:27:37,072 --> 00:27:38,192
There's nothing to be angry about.

487
00:27:41,552 --> 00:27:42,832
You were perfectly fine just now.

488
00:27:43,391 --> 00:27:44,871
Why did you suddenly change?

489
00:27:45,391 --> 00:27:48,912
It's because I saw something
I shouldn't have seen.

490
00:27:50,351 --> 00:27:51,432
What did you see?

491
00:27:51,552 --> 00:27:53,511
I saw you and Lv Beiyi
having unresolved feelings.

492
00:27:53,952 --> 00:27:55,511
You were deeply attached to each other.

493
00:27:56,511 --> 00:27:57,952
What did you see?

494
00:27:59,552 --> 00:28:01,591
I was so anxious to find Shuilan,

495
00:28:01,591 --> 00:28:02,680
which caused pain in my abdomen.

496
00:28:02,952 --> 00:28:05,952
Lv Beiyi happened to pass by
and checked on me.

497
00:28:07,751 --> 00:28:08,672
My belly hurts.

498
00:28:08,832 --> 00:28:10,792
Don't use the child as a shield.

499
00:28:10,991 --> 00:28:11,730
Your belly is hurting?

500
00:28:11,871 --> 00:28:12,912
Should I summon Lv Beiyi

501
00:28:13,032 --> 00:28:14,792
to feel your belly
and help you feel better?

502
00:28:14,792 --> 00:28:15,231
You...

503
00:28:15,751 --> 00:28:17,792
All right, you two are so close.

504
00:28:18,351 --> 00:28:20,471
Why did you act so affectionately
towards me just now?

505
00:28:20,552 --> 00:28:21,832
You asked me to feel this child

506
00:28:21,832 --> 00:28:22,832
and listen to it.

507
00:28:22,952 --> 00:28:24,471
It's because you are the child's father,

508
00:28:25,192 --> 00:28:27,231
I did what I was supposed to do.

509
00:28:27,871 --> 00:28:29,511
Am I really the child's father?

510
00:28:31,780 --> 00:28:33,511
You said you only did what
you were supposed to do.

511
00:28:33,511 --> 00:28:34,912
So let me tell you
what I should do.

512
00:28:34,912 --> 00:28:35,631
You don't deserve.

513
00:28:35,631 --> 00:28:36,552
So when the child is born,

514
00:28:36,552 --> 00:28:37,952
you won't be his mother!

515
00:28:41,111 --> 00:28:41,952
What are you saying?

516
00:28:45,432 --> 00:28:45,952
Miss!

517
00:28:45,952 --> 00:28:46,991
- Miss.
- Miss!

518
00:28:46,991 --> 00:28:47,351
Ms. Lian

519
00:28:47,351 --> 00:28:48,432
Miss!

520
00:28:48,432 --> 00:28:49,072
Ms. Lian

521
00:28:49,072 --> 00:28:49,871
Let's go back.

522
00:28:49,991 --> 00:28:50,631
Let's go back first

523
00:28:50,631 --> 00:28:51,832
and then deal with others.

524
00:28:51,832 --> 00:28:52,432
Yes, Ms. Lian.

525
00:28:52,432 --> 00:28:53,072
It's cold.

526
00:28:53,072 --> 00:28:54,312
You'll catch a cold.

527
00:28:54,471 --> 00:28:55,991
I can't be the mother of this child?

528
00:28:56,792 --> 00:28:57,751
When the child is born,

529
00:28:58,511 --> 00:28:59,511
it won't call me mother.

530
00:29:00,591 --> 00:29:01,912
It'll call someone else mother,

531
00:29:01,912 --> 00:29:03,032
just like Shi'er.

532
00:29:03,312 --> 00:29:04,032
- No, Miss.
- No, Ms. Lian.

533
00:29:04,032 --> 00:29:04,871
It won't.

534
00:29:05,072 --> 00:29:05,871
It is your child.

535
00:29:05,871 --> 00:29:07,032
Why would it call someone else?

536
00:29:07,032 --> 00:29:07,471
Yes, Miss.

537
00:29:07,471 --> 00:29:08,591
Let go of me!

538
00:29:09,871 --> 00:29:10,912
- Miss!
- Ms. Lian!

539
00:29:55,111 --> 00:29:56,471
Miss!

540
00:29:56,832 --> 00:29:57,832
What happened to you? Miss!

541
00:29:58,231 --> 00:29:58,792
Miss!

542
00:29:59,952 --> 00:30:00,591
What happened?

543
00:30:02,591 --> 00:30:04,591
Help! Please!

544
00:30:04,991 --> 00:30:06,751
Miss.

545
00:30:07,552 --> 00:30:10,351
Help!

546
00:30:26,672 --> 00:30:29,271
When Ms. Lian's anger subsides,

547
00:30:30,111 --> 00:30:32,111
I'll accompany you

548
00:30:32,111 --> 00:30:33,511
to apologise to her tomorrow.

549
00:30:34,271 --> 00:30:35,552
She's a reasonable person.

550
00:30:36,952 --> 00:30:38,832
I'm sure you'll reconcile.

551
00:30:42,111 --> 00:30:42,912
Please, Young Master,

552
00:30:42,912 --> 00:30:43,591
don't be angry.

553
00:30:43,591 --> 00:30:44,770
Getting angry will hurt your health.

554
00:30:45,792 --> 00:30:48,111
Being indifferent can hurt others,

555
00:30:49,591 --> 00:30:50,751
but being too deeply involved

556
00:30:52,032 --> 00:30:53,072
can hurt yourself.

557
00:30:53,432 --> 00:30:54,432
Too deeply involved?

558
00:30:55,631 --> 00:30:56,991
She's not even aware of it!

559
00:30:59,552 --> 00:31:00,710
As long as you have the intention,

560
00:31:01,432 --> 00:31:03,152
you'll eventually get what you want.

