00:32:52,032 --> 00:32:52,952
The crying of a baby.

580
00:32:53,430 --> 00:32:53,871
Young Master.

581
00:32:53,871 --> 00:32:54,631
There's a baby crying.

582
00:32:54,631 --> 00:32:55,832
Young Master, you're drunk.

583
00:32:56,712 --> 00:32:57,152
There's...

584
00:32:59,152 --> 00:32:59,672
There's a sound.

585
00:33:00,952 --> 00:33:01,672
- Master.
